00:28:10,485 --> 00:28:13,784
<i>[#</i> Something Corporate:
<i>21 And Invincible]</i>

431
00:28:33,775 --> 00:28:36,801
<i>[Tulloch] I know I've probably ruined</i>
<i>my chances of being the skipper.</i>

432
00:28:36,844 --> 00:28:39,472
<i>Now I just have to hope</i>
<i>I'll still make the race.</i>

433
00:28:41,249 --> 00:28:43,717
- [shouting]
- [laughing]

434
00:28:54,128 --> 00:28:56,961
<i>[Brant-Zawadzki] Genny's a great sailor</i>
<i>and won't have any trouble</i>

