00:28:56,998 --> 00:28:59,489
<i>getting back to sailing the boat</i>
<i>when she recovers.</i>

436
00:28:59,534 --> 00:29:01,331
<i>I don't think she should be punished,</i>

437
00:29:01,369 --> 00:29:04,133
<i>because having to miss out</i>
<i>on all the sailing this session</i>

438
00:29:04,172 --> 00:29:06,333
<i>is way more punishment</i>
<i>than anyone deserves.</i>

439
00:29:06,374 --> 00:29:08,342
<i>So, yeah, it sucks all around.</i>

440
00:29:12,814 --> 00:29:15,305
By the end of it, the kids
were pretty comfortable

