00:30:08,936 --> 00:30:12,463
I have complete confidence
in Jeremy as the skipper.

455
00:30:12,507 --> 00:30:14,099
Troll, hands down.

456
00:30:14,142 --> 00:30:15,507
Yeah, Troll.
Troll, yeah.

457
00:30:15,543 --> 00:30:17,909
Aussie's got my vote, too.

458
00:30:17,945 --> 00:30:21,176
- Uh, Troll...
- [laughter]

459
00:30:22,950 --> 00:30:24,850
I definitely want you to be the skipper

460
00:30:24,886 --> 00:30:27,184
because the crap you say
when... [bleep]... goes wrong

461
00:30:27,221 --> 00:30:28,916
- is just so funny.
- [laughter]

462
00:30:28,956 --> 00:30:31,322
It's funny. So, I mean, I think, like...

463
00:30:31,359 --> 00:30:33,759
<i>[Wilmot] I didn't expect</i>
<i>the decision to be unanimous.</i>

464
00:30:33,795 --> 00:30:36,457
