I love sailing with all of you guys.

465
00:30:36,497 --> 00:30:39,057
I-I respect every one of you so much.

466
00:30:39,100 --> 00:30:42,797
And it would be a huge honor...

467
00:30:42,837 --> 00:30:46,170
<i>[Wilmot] I feel like, when the decision</i>
