00:34:03,371 --> 00:34:07,000
<i>[Will] It's almost impossible</i>
<i>to explain how unhappy I was.</i>

535
00:34:08,309 --> 00:34:10,800
<i>I wanted to call a cab,</i>
<i>go to the airport,</i>

536
00:34:10,845 --> 00:34:12,836
<i>fly standby out of that place.</i>

537
00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:15,974
If I didn't think, like, the weight
would slow us down that much,

538
00:34:16,017 --> 00:34:18,815
I'd throw another life raft on the boat.

539
00:34:18,853 --> 00:34:22,118
But you know this was gonna happen
since the start.

540
00:34:25,593 --> 00:34:28,756
<i>[Will] I didn't understand</i>
<i>Jeremy's choice at the time.</i>

541
00:34:29,730 --> 00:34:31,061
<i>I don't think I ever will.</i>

542
00:34:35,403 --> 00:34:38,304
