00:35:46,974 --> 00:35:49,306
<i>He does it so efficiently,</i>
<i>you don't notice him.</i>

564
00:35:49,343 --> 00:35:51,834
<i>So he's the type of guy</i>
<i>who can just slip through.</i>

565
00:35:51,879 --> 00:35:54,712
