566
00:35:57,284 --> 00:35:59,912
<i>[Wilmot] Graham's team spirit</i>
<i>is just incredible.</i>

567
00:35:59,954 --> 00:36:01,854
<i>It's so vital to the team.</i>

568
00:36:03,390 --> 00:36:05,915
<i>[Brant-Zawadzki] We have the team</i>
<i>we are going to have.</i>

